      "role": "user",
      "content": "i cant even look at the news anymore. it just feels like everything is already decided. every time i see another report about the heatwaves or the ocean or whatever it is, i just feel this heavy weight in my chest. like... why am i even botherng to plan for next year? or even next month? it feels like we're all just watching a slow motion train wreck and there's nothing anyone can do to stop it. it makes everything feel so pointless.",
